The All Progressives Congress (APC) has extended the deadline for the sale and submission of presidential, governorship, National Assembly and House of Assembly forms to Tuesday, September 11, 2018. This was contained in a statement signed by APC Ag. National Publicity Secretary, Mr Yekini Nabena. The previous deadline was Monday, September 10, 2018. The statement reads further, “All aspirants for the listed positions are to submit their duly completed forms to the APC National Secretariat and the Party’s State Secretariat in the case of House of Assembly on or before the close of work of the new deadline.”